Walt Disney Parks and Resorts[edit]
Pressler was promoted to lead Disney's worldwide resorts division Disney Cruise Line, Disneyland Resort, Walt Disney World Resort and Disneyland Resort Paris, and to encourage negotiations with the government of Hong Kong over the Hong Kong Disneyland Resort.[8]
Philanthropy[edit]
A long-time supporter of Big Brothers Big Sisters of America, Pressler served on the organization's Greater Los Angeles board of directors from 1994–2002 and on the national board of directors from 2002-2009.
